#: ../../neopixel.rst:14
msgid ""
"From our tests, the Microbit NeoPixel module can drive up to around 256 "
"NeoPixels. Anything above that and you may experience weird bugs and "
"issues. The micro:bit can only supply 90mA **V1** or 190mA **V2**  to "
